Package cop3330.misc

package cop3330.misc
Optional. Contains miscellaneous helper classes primarily for UI table models based on GenericList.

This package includes table model implementations for displaying domain objects such as Course and Student.

Note: Classes in this package are intended as helper utilities for the user interface and do not contain core business logic. They should be ignored during formal code reviews or evaluations focusing on main application functionality.

  • Classes
    Class
    Description
    CourseListModel
    A table model for displaying a list of Course objects.
    GenericListModel<T extends Searchable<T>>
    An abstract table model backed by a generic GenericList of elements that implement the Searchable interface.
    StudentListModel
    A table model for displaying a list of Student objects.
